OL,5, Six former Metropolitan Police officers
OL,6, have been given suspended prison       
OL,7, sentences for sending racist, sexist   
OL,8, and homophobic messages on WhatsApp,   
OL,9, after a BBC Newsnight investigation.   
OL,11,FDeputy chief magistrate Tan Ikram said 
OL,12,Fthey had harmed public confidence in   
OL,13,Fthe police.                            
OL,15,FHe did not accept a suggestion that    
OL,16,Ftheir views were merely "antiquated".  
OL,18,FThey were not serving officers during  
OL,19,Ftheir participation in the group,      
OL,20,FWestminster Magistrates' Court heard.  
